--------------080209000202020802000006
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=us-ascii; format=flowed
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit

This patch adds ippp filters to isdn similar to ppp filters
(active-filter & pass-filter). Also included is the required
patch for ipppd. You need to run autoconf in the ipppd subdir
before compiling. ipppd support is enabled with --enable-ippp-filter.

Comments and suggestions are welcome.
 
Regards,
Patrick



